<sup>e</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Carlson%20MC"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id7"><span class="name western">Michelle C Carlson</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id7">
<h3><span class="name western">Michelle C Carlson</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>b</sup>Department of Mental Health, Johns Hopkins University, Bloomberg School of Public Health, Baltimore, MD, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Carlson%20MC"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Michelle C Carlson</span></a>
